00_TEMPLATE_REVIEW_FINDINGS.md

# === Source directories that share a name with the runtime-output rules above ===
# The broad `profiles/`, `reports/`, `instances/`, `storage/`, `data/` rules (kept above so they
# still ignore any runtime-generated directory) ALSO matched these real SOURCE directories, which
# left required source files untracked and missing from the repo. Re-include the source trees
# explicitly; the sensitive/output patterns above (e.g. session-profiles.json, *.storageState.json,
# user-data-dir/) still apply to actual runtime artifacts.
!src/profiles/
!src/reports/
!src/instances/
!src/storage/
!src/data/
!app/renderer/components/instances/
!app/renderer/components/reports/
.benchmark-runtime/

# Phase 5 observability UI walkthrough fixtures (seeded DBs; regenerate with seed-observability-fixtures.mts)
.fixtures-observability/
